<dl id="n12126a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12126a">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12126a"> 126(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> take mother&apos;s name</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Il est &agrave; noter que Vincent devrait ainsi s&apos;appeler Vincent Lopez, le nom de Ferrer lui venant de son ascendance f&eacute;minine. <br><font color="green">[We should note that Vincent was supposed to be called Vincent Lopez, the name of Ferrer came through the female line.]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 3n1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
